{
  "stem": "6777.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've been there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes and no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For example, the Polish students-- [NON-ENGLISH] what-- association-- they had been very, very nationalistic, and of course against Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at the same time, they've been very much against Jews and partly England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's took place after the start of the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans had declared war on Poland and even before they came-- before the news came over the radio that the war was on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had, already, airplanes bombing us before the official declaration.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 1st of September, '39.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and at the same time the German had declared war over the air-- over the radio-- that was the first day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next day or two, I -- I don't remember exactly anymore-- then England came in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's when the demonstration took place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the 1st of September, we had been back in Warsaw from a summers-- uh, what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Summer house or-- from holiday, summer holidays.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd been coming back from college because I'd been doing certification in college.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Vera and her husband and the children and the grandmother they've been in a suburb of Warsaw in a little villa.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we all came back into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, Vera's husband got called up, mobilized.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a Polish army officer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Israel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Israel Furst.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was an officer of the Polish army, so of course he got called up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he provided for us quite a bit of food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A bag of rice, a bag of flour, a bag of this and that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And not very far from us, around the corner, there was a very big hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after the first few bombings, that hospital got bombed.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
